---
title: Easy One-Pot Cheesy Chorizo & Cherry Tomato Stew with Israeli Couscous & Parsley
description: A saucy chorizo stew with soffritto and leek does wonders to add flavour on top of fluffy and soft couscous. Serving up chorizo and couscous together brings a balance to dinner time that we crave.

*We’ve replaced the couscous in this recipe with Israeli due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
